    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长莱恩称通胀率重返 2% 目标尚无定论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/ecb-s-lane-says-return-to-2-inflation-target-isn-t-secure-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧洲央行让通胀率回升至 2% 的斗争尚未胜利，利率必须维持在必要的高位才能实现这一目标，同时又不能对经济造成过度损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/ecb-s-lane-says-return-to-2-inflation-target-isn-t-secure-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 16:52:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
